headline: Azelis: Transparency Notification From Invesco Ltd.
summary: ANTWERP, Belgium, October 08, 2025--Regulatory News: In accordance with Article 14 of the Belgian Transparency law of May 2, 2007, Azelis Group NV (Brussels:AZE) announces that it has received a transparency notification from Invesco Ltd.
